Package gal4j.algorithm

Class Config

java.lang.Object
gal4j.algorithm.Config
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultConfig
public class Config extends Object
Configuration class for genetic algorithm parameters. This class stores various configuration values used during the execution of the genetic algorithm, such as population size, mutation rate, number of generations, and others.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Filip KÅ™enek
